text.tspan: attaches two objects by "pinning" them together
at an anchor point which they may revolve around
constrains two objects so that the distance
between the two anchor points is constant
maxMotorTorque (maximum motor torque - how hard it turns)
length (desired length of the spring / distance)
frequencyHz (the frequency of the oscillation, less than 30)
dampingRatio (1 = no oscillation, less than 1, allows oscillation)
designed for use with Matrox TripleHead2Go
